  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7933994/" class="title-link">主席光辉永耀</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7933994"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/73078707/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/73078707/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">JianBo</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-06-11"
      class="main-meta">2016-06-11 14:51:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7933994_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  主席是最富有智慧的。当创业史来读，一穷二白，用信仰战胜了拥有百万大军的帝国主义支持的国军。忒不容易了，胜利太来之不易了。主席自始至终注重两个问题：军队和土地。这也让我们理解了现在诸多的国策。邓也是主席培养的对象，淮海战役这么多兵与将交与他指挥，军中位置不差...

